OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FA Denbighshire man on trial for rape
OL,7,Fhas admitted having sex with a 15-year-
OL,8,Fold girl but said it was consensual
OL,9,Fand believed she was older.
OL,11,FZiaullah Badshah, now 25, is one of
OL,12,Ffour men facing charges of child
OL,13,Fsexual exploitation and trafficking.
OL,15,FBadshah, of Brighton Road, Rhyl,
OL,16,Fdenies two counts of conspiracy to
OL,17,Ftraffic, two counts of rape, two
OL,18,Fcounts of conspiracy to require a
OL,19,Fperson to perform compulsory labour
OL,20,Fand supplying cannabis to another.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
