PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,F"I would never go with an underage
OL,7,Fgirl," he said, while giving evidence
OL,8,Ffor the first time at Caernarfon Crown
OL,9,FCourt on Wednesday (17 June).
OL,11,FFrom the witness box he told jurors he
OL,12,Fmoved to Rhyl from Pakistan 10 years
OL,13,Fago. He left at the age of 15 after a
OL,14,Ffamily member was killed and his home
OL,15,Fdestroyed.
