PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FHe was evacuated to be with his
OL,7,Fbrother, who lived in the north Wales
OL,8,Fseaside town. It was here he got to
OL,9,Fknow the other men in the dock Mustafa
OL,10,FIqbal, Mohamed Arshad and Jaswinder
OL,11,FSingh.
OL,13,FIt is the prosecution's case that
OL,14,Fthree girls, aged 16 and under, were
OL,15,Ftargeted by Mustafa Iqbal, Mohamed
OL,16,FArshad, Ziaullah Badshah and Jaswinder
OL,17,FSingh, who acted as a grooming gang.
OL,18,FThey all deny the charges against them.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
