FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FBadshah told jurors he has depression,
OL,7,Fanxiety and PTSD for which he has
OL,8,Freceived psychiatric help and
OL,9,Fmedication.
OL,11,FHe said he met Child B and Child C in
OL,12,F2022 at the home of Mustafa Iqbal on
OL,13,FTrellewelyn Road. He called there with
OL,14,FMohamed Arshad as they drove home from
OL,15,FChester.
OL,17,FHe told jurors he had never met the 15
OL,18,Fand 14-year-old before.
OL,20,FHe said: "I didn't know them. It was
OL,21,Fthe first time I saw them there."
