PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FHe admitted they smoked cannabis and
OL,7,Fplayed spin the bottle. Defence
OL,8,Fbarrister Simon Killeen asked Badshah:
OL,9,F"Did you kiss (Child B and C)?"
OL,11,F"Yes," he responded.
OL,13,FMr Killeen added: "Was there any
OL,14,Fdiscussion about how old they were?"
OL,16,FHe answered: "They said they were 17."
