FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FIt is the prosecution's case that none
OL,7,Fof the defendants investigated the
OL,8,Fgirls ages and in the case of Iqbal
OL,9,Fand Arshad, evidence has been heard
OL,10,Fthat they lied about their ages to
OL,11,Fmake them appear younger.
OL,13,FBadshah told the jury that he had sex
OL,14,Fwith Child B at his home in April 2022
OL,15,Fbut it was consensual. He said he only
OL,16,Fdiscovered she was 15 when she had
OL,17,Fgone to London with co-defendant
OL,18,FJaswinder Singh.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
