FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1781704086
OL,3,CMan accused of rape claims he thought
OL,4,C15-year-old girl was older
OL,6,FSingh, 65, is charged with two counts
OL,7,Fof conspiracy to traffic and supplying
OL,8,Fcannabis to another. He has pleaded
OL,9,Fnot guilty.
OL,11,FBecoming tearful, Badshah told the
OL,12,Fjury: "That was one of the worst
OL,13,Ftimes... it's something I would never
OL,14,Fdo... underage girls and dating them."
OL,16,FThe trial continues.
